  "title": "Sales Engineer (Science) #HZO",
  "description": "<p>Location: Jurong East <br />Salary: Up to $3.8K + Comms </p><p><strong>Job Scope: </strong></p><ul><li>Prospect and generate new leads</li><li>Develop and maintain relationships with existing and potential customers</li><li>Regularly conduct seminars, product demonstrations and technical presentations to customers and prospects</li><li>Develop sales proposals and negotiate contracts</li><li>Meet or exceed monthly and annual sales targets</li><li>Meet or exceed weekly sales activities targets</li><li>Collaborate with the marketing team to develop and implement effective sales strategies</li><li>Monitor industry trends and provide feedback to the sales and marketing teams</li><li>Attend trade shows and industry events to network and generate leads</li></ul><p><strong>Job Requirements:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Min. Degree in science/ engineering/ any relevant field </li><li>Familiarity with CRM software and sales tools</li></ul><p><br />For interested applicants, please send your updated resume to: melissa@recruitexpress.com.sg</p><p>All candidates’ information will be treated with the strictest confidence</p><p>Melissa Zhang Zhiqi (Mezzo)</p><p>R2197564</p><p>Recruit Express Pte Ltd</p><p>99C4599</p>",
